edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtf

Class CasMappings

  • edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtf.CasMappings

  • public class CasMappings

    Mappings from RTF elements to UIMA CAS elements. Is a POJO/bean that is XML-serializable via JAXB.
